<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Master Model Release – <%= (profile && profile.legal_name) ? profile.legal_name : (user && user.username ? user.username : 'Model') %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  <style>
    body { background:#111; color:#fafafa; }
    .print-container { max-width: 860px; margin: 2rem auto; background:#181818; padding:2rem; border-radius: 14px; }
    h1, h2 { text-align:center; margin: 0.25rem 0; }
    .legal-block { margin:1rem 0; line-height:1.55; font-size:0.95rem; color:#e8e8f2; }
    .signature-box { margin-top:2rem; padding-top: 1rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12); }
    .meta-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; margin-top: 1rem; }
    .meta-grid p { margin: 0.25rem 0; }
    .mono { font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, "Liberation Mono", "Courier New", monospace; font-size: 0.85rem; }
    @media print {
      body { background:#fff; color:#000; }
      .print-container { background:#fff; color:#000; box-shadow:none; border-radius: 0; }
      .no-print { display:none; }
      .legal-block { color:#000; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="print-container">
    <div class="no-print" style="text-align:right;">
      <button class="btn secondary" onclick="window.print()">Print / Save as PDF</button>
    </div>

    <h1>LumenNyx Studios</h1>
    <h2>Master Model Release &amp; Grant of Rights</h2>

    <div class="meta-grid">
      <div>
        <p><strong>Performer / Model:</strong>
          <%= (profile && profile.legal_name) ? profile.legal_name : (user && user.username ? user.username : '—') %>
        </p>
        <p><strong>Aliases / Stage Names:</strong> <%= (profile && profile.aliases) ? profile.aliases : '—' %></p>
        <p><strong>Date of Birth:</strong> <%= (profile && profile.date_of_birth) ? profile.date_of_birth : '—' %></p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <% if (typeof CONTACT_EMAILS !== 'undefined' && CONTACT_EMAILS) { %>
          <p><strong>Studio Contact (Releases):</strong> <%= CONTACT_EMAILS.release %></p>
          <p><strong>2257 / Records:</strong> <%= CONTACT_EMAILS['2257'] || CONTACT_EMAILS.compliance2257 || '—' %></p>
          <p><strong>Legal Notices:</strong> <%= CONTACT_EMAILS.legal %></p>
        <% } else { %>
          <p><strong>Studio Contact (Releases):</strong> release@lumennyxstudios.com</p>
          <p><strong>2257 / Records:</strong> 2257@lumennyxstudios.com</p>
          <p><strong>Legal Notices:</strong> legal@lumennyxstudios.com</p>
        <% } %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-block">
      This document is a general grant of rights by the performer to LumenNyx Studios (the “Producer”).
      It is intended for adult-oriented photo and video content produced in the United States with
      performers who are 18 years of age or older.
    </div>

    <div class="legal-block">
      1. <strong>Age &amp; Identity.</strong> The performer affirms they are at least eighteen (18) years of age,
      that identifying information and documentation provided to Producer is true and correct, and that valid
      government-issued photo identification has been presented for record-keeping in accordance with U.S. federal
      record rules (including 18 U.S.C. § 2257 and related regulations, where applicable).
    </div>

    <div class="legal-block">
      2. <strong>Grant of Rights.</strong> The performer grants to Producer a perpetual, worldwide, transferable license
      to record, reproduce, edit, adapt, publicly display, distribute, advertise, and otherwise exploit photo or video
      content created during shoots with Producer, in any media now known or later developed, subject to any written restrictions
      agreed separately in individual booking or scene agreements.
    </div>

    <div class="legal-block">
      3. <strong>Use of Name &amp; Likeness.</strong> The performer authorizes Producer to use their legal name, stage names,
      likeness, voice, and biographical material in connection with the advertising, marketing, and exploitation of the content,
      except where restricted in writing.
    </div>

    <div class="legal-block">
      4. <strong>Independent Contractor Status.</strong> The performer understands they are engaged as an independent contractor,
      not an employee, and is responsible for their own taxes and reporting obligations.
    </div>

    <div class="legal-block">
      5. <strong>Revocation / Takedown Requests.</strong> Producer will reasonably consider written requests from the performer regarding
      removal or limited distribution of content, but no guarantee of removal from all platforms or archives is made.
      Any agreed takedowns or modifications will be confirmed in writing.
    </div>

    <div class="legal-block">
      6. <strong>Governing Law.</strong> This release is intended to be interpreted under the laws of the State of New York,
      without regard to conflict-of-law principles.
    </div>

    <div class="legal-block">
      <em>Important:</em> This document is provided for record-keeping and clarity and is not individualized legal advice.
      Performers and Producer should consult their own attorney regarding their rights and obligations.
    </div>

    <div class="signature-box">
      <% if (release) { %>
        <p><strong>Performer signature on file:</strong> <%= release.signed_name || '—' %></p>
        <p><strong>Signed at (timestamp):</strong> <%= release.signed_at || '—' %></p>
        <p><strong>IP address recorded:</strong> <span class="mono"><%= release.ip_address || '—' %></span></p>
        <p><strong>User-Agent recorded:</strong> <span class="mono"><%= release.user_agent || '—' %></span></p>
      <% } else { %>
        <p><strong>Status:</strong> No master release is on file for this model.</p>
      <% } %>

      <p><strong>Internal reference ID:</strong> Model #<%= user && user.id ? user.id : '—' %></p>
    </div>

    <div class="signature-box">
      <p><strong>Producer / Studio:</strong> LumenNyx Studios (Wallkill, NY region)</p>
      <% if (typeof CONTACT_EMAILS !== 'undefined' && CONTACT_EMAILS) { %>
        <p><strong>General Contact:</strong> <%= CONTACT_EMAILS.contact || 'contact@lumennyxstudios.com' %></p>
      <% } else { %>
        <p><strong>General Contact:</strong> contact@lumennyxstudios.com</p>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
